1
00:00:24,030 --> 00:00:25,290
[Adapted from a novel published on
Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:27,180
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:28,300 --> 00:00:29,830
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:31,550
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:14,350 --> 00:02:19,480
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:24,790
[Previously]

7
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,800
Chen Changsheng is indeed a director.

8
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,660
Grand Pontiff,

9
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,680
your judgment is truly exceptional.

10
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,320
Luo.

11
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,480
We're here to pick you up
for the Imperial Court Exam.

12
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,410
Do you want to go?

13
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:34,850
He wants to compete with all the geniuses
in the Imperial Court Exam

14
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,840
and aim for first place!

15
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:36,820
[Chen Changsheng]

16
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,440
Chen Changsheng.

17
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,920
At the Imperial Court Exam,

18
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,690
I'll take you down a peg!

19
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,760
Chen Changsheng is really bold.

20
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,770
Now that I've said that,

21
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:50,040
I'll be the target of everyone
in the Imperial Court Exam.

22
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,800
The Imperial Court Exam hasn't even begun.

23
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:57,800
Yet, Director Chen and the State Religious Academy
have already become everyone's target.

24
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,600
Would this...

25
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,080
be too much pressure?

26
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,040
Only by drawing strength from all sides

27
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,960
and being the focus of all eyes

28
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:09,760
can he grow faster.

29
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,800
I still can't sense the starlight
in my body.

30
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:18,320
Is it because my meridians
differ from others?

31
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,640
If I didn't absorb it,

32
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,600
then where did
all that starlight go?

33
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:23,560
[Four Scriptures of Seated Illumination]

34
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,760
The only way to figure this out

35
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,370
is to perform Seated Illumination
and observe myself.

36
00:03:25,370 --> 00:03:30,320
[Having tenuous True Essence is akin
to self-immolation; one ends as dust]

37
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,640
But if I skip Marrow Cleansing

38
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,960
and force Seated Illumination,

39
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,090
it's very likely...

40
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,640
Without Seated Illumination,
I can't find the starlight.

41
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,600
But if I perform Seated Illumination,

42
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,200
I might burn myself to death.

43
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,960
What a headache.

44
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,280
Lights?

45
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,800
Is that Luo?

46
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,450
It's my savior by the cold pool.

47
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,640
I thought an old acquaintance returned.

48
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,960
I have been most presumptuous.

49
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,490
Please forgive me, Senior.

50
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:57,360
Could she be deaf-mute

51
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,480
like Senior?

52
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,120
No wonder she didn't react

53
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,050
when the flowerpot fell
last time.

54
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:08,640
Thank you.

55
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,960
Rizhu Snow Bud tea.

56
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,460
Senior drinks this often too.

57
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:20,360
The fragrance of the tea
has calmed my heart.

58
00:04:18,779 --> 00:04:23,620
[Herbal tea flourishes in
the Liangzhe regions.
Among them, Rizhu ranks supreme.]

59
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,640
I only have a chance to succeed

60
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,600
at the Imperial Court Exam
if I achieve Seated Illumination.

61
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:27,130
Actually, I had no choice
from the beginning.

62
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,760
Since I know the risk,

63
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,760
I'll finish what remains first.

64
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,400
Excuse me.

65
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,860
Senior, do you know

66
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,540
how to find that cold pool?

67
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,600
You're not afraid of death?

68
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,020
I don't want to die.

69
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:42,020
But keeping promises is very important.

70
00:04:46,980 --> 00:04:49,500
[Ice]

71
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,360
Ladies and gentlemen!

72
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:52,090
[Tianxiang Pavilion]

73
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,560
The betting
for the Jiachen-year Imperial Court Exam

74
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,000
has begun!

75
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,280
Gou Hanshi will surely take first place!

76
00:05:02,110 --> 00:05:03,560
[Gou Hanshi]

77
00:05:03,650 --> 00:05:05,070
[Zhuang Huanyu]

78
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,160
Tiandao Academy is the strongest.

79
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,400
Divine Nation's Seven Prodigies will win!

80
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:06,050
[Tang Thirty-Six] [Luo]

81
00:05:06,050 --> 00:05:06,680
[Tang Thirty-Six] [Zhe Xiu]

82
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,400
Go Tianhai Shengxue!

83
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,640
Teach those southerners
a lesson!

84
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:09,880
[Liu Chongshan] [Guan Feibai]

85
00:05:09,910 --> 00:05:10,590
[Tianhai Shengxue]

86
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,160
Each candidate has different capabilities,

87
00:05:10,650 --> 00:05:13,140
[Luo] [Zhe Xiu] [Tang Thirty-Six]

88
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,400
so the odds differ.

89
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,160
If you want a small bet for a big win,

90
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,680
you can try an underdog,

91
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,800
Chen Changsheng
from the State Religious Academy

92
00:05:17,490 --> 00:05:18,640
[Chen Changsheng]

93
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:22,190
swore he'll win first place.

94
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,960
Get out of here.

95
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,160
As if he's worthy?

96
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,680
Swearing to be first
at a mere Marrow Cleansing realm?

97
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,960
What a joke.

98
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:30,600
Exactly.

99
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,440
Anyone betting on him is a complete idiot.

100
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,120
Interesting.

101
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,420
I just love betting on underdogs.

102
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,120
As long as you all

103
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,159
can afford to play.

104
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,159
Betting on Chen Changsheng

105
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:43,960
is basically giving money away.

106
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,280
Is this guy crazy?

107
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,960
Keep your voice down.

108
00:05:46,590 --> 00:05:48,360
[Chen Changsheng]

109
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,670
He's the young master
of the Tang family in Wenshui.

110
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:49,220
See?

111
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:51,170
Listen to me and you won't go wrong!

112
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:55,760
Push Chen Changsheng and the State Religious Academy
to number one on the board.

113
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:57,900
[Luo] [Chen Changsheng] [Tang Thirty-Six]

114
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,120
Chen Changsheng.

115
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:01,120
I was so cool today.

116
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,100
You should've seen the scene.

117
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:10,120
Sir went out for an appointment.

118
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,480
Can you stop yelling?

119
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,410
An appointment?

120
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,600
In this city,

121
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,730
there are people he knows that I don't?

122
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,160
Ice.

123
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,280
In a huge city like Shendu,

124
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,280
it's very common.

125
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,080
I thought finding clues
would be difficult.

126
00:06:22,610 --> 00:06:24,470
[Zhang Ji Sugar Painting]

127
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,540
But unexpectedly,

128
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,920
the moment I mention ice,

129
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,980
everyone will tell me the same place.

130
00:06:29,150 --> 00:06:30,590
The biggest ice market in the Shendu,

131
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:32,570
[West Market Hutong]

132
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,250
West Market Hutong.

133
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,640
Beixin Bridge.

134
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:33,730
[Beixin Bridge]

135
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,530
The ancient well there.

136
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,520
The entrance

137
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,690
is actually in broad daylight.

138
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,080
I came to the right place.

139
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:07,720
Senior!

140
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,720
It's me.

141
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,680
In Dragon Race years,

142
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,090
I should call him...

143
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,370
Master Long.

144
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,010
I, Chen Changsheng,

145
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,050
have come to keep the appointment.

146
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:22,250
[Master Long]

147
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,600
Senior.

148
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,960
Please don't be angry.

149
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,360
Did I offend you somehow?

150
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,000
Is this how

151
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,800
a dragon sounds?

152
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,159
Since you kept your promise,

153
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,320
I'll overlook

154
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,400
your offense just now.

155
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:55,110
[The last Frost Dragon]

156
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,570
It's actually a young girl.

157
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,130
Makes sense.

158
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,159
The Dragon Race has long lifespans.

159
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,820
I assumed things too quickly.

160
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,520
Thank you for helping me
last time, Senior.

161
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,800
If there's anything I can do,

162
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,440
go ahead.

163
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,040
Well,

164
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,840
I helped you escape last time.

165
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:08,840
This time,

166
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,760
it's your turn to help me escape.

167
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,450
These talismans

168
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,040
use the dragon language.

169
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,760
To break this formation,

170
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:24,040
we need to understand the meaning
of these in dragon language first.

171
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,160
That's easy.

172
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,560
I'll teach you the dragon language

173
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,160
and you help me break the formation.

174
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,800
Master Zhice's formation...

175
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,920
I can't guarantee success.

176
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,049
But I will do my best.

177
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,159
Senior.

178
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,320
Let's start.

179
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,200
Wait.

180
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,580
Before we start...

181
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,559
Well...

182
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,799
Help me with one more small favor.

183
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:48,350
[Nothing is greater than meat]

184
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:49,200
It's been 500 years.

185
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,520
I'm finally eating meat!

186
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,160
What did this kid do

187
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,600
for Master Zhice to imprison her
for so long

188
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:00,060
and not even give her meat?

189
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,480
I'm full.

190
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:05,720
Come on!

191
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,040
Let's break this formation!

192
00:09:09,530 --> 00:09:13,100
Step one, dragon language vocal training.

193
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:15,040
That's not right.

194
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,710
Use your diaphragm.

195
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:21,570
[Warm, jade, glowing]

196
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:31,780
Silly bear.

197
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,160
Is Chen Changsheng back?

198
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,800
The director just took a shower,

199
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,720
changed clothes

200
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,400
and headed out again.

201
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,080
What?

202
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,360
Again?

203
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,200
The Imperial Court Exam is in half a month.

204
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,800
What's he busy with outside?

205
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,440
The Imperial Court Exam is almost here,

206
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,160
yet this guy keeps going to appointments.

207
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,640
Could he be losing focus in pleasures?

208
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,360
The director wakes up early
and comes home late every day.

209
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,600
He always looks in a hurry.

210
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,280
It must be something important.

211
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:09,390
Step two, decipher dragon script.

212
00:10:17,850 --> 00:10:19,060
[Fierce, battle, courage]

213
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:29,480
The basic array patterns

214
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,680
have been sorted out.

215
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,280
Next,

216
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,150
only execution will reveal the result.

217
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:37,240
Step three, break the formation.

218
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,320
How confident are you?

219
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,920
30%.

220
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,400
It's been 500 years.

221
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:47,000
I don't want to wait
in this dark place anymore.

222
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:48,750
I don't have True Essence.

223
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,890
I can only use the golden needle
to mark positions

224
00:10:50,890 --> 00:10:52,690
to help you break the formation.

225
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,100
West three.

226
00:10:56,430 --> 00:10:57,160
East two.

227
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,410
Hold steady.

228
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:01,040
Connect them together.

229
00:11:01,660 --> 00:11:02,320
Reverse it.

230
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:04,450
Then, North four.

231
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:05,770
South one.

232
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:08,650
Inject your True Essence at the same time.

233
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:10,290
Rotate separately.

234
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,120
Carefully withdraw.

235
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:16,980
Now!

236
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:36,640
Chen Changsheng!

237
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:38,030
We did it!

238
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,920
Although we only solved one array pattern,

239
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:42,360
we're going in the right direction.

240
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,560
If we keep trying,

241
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:44,880
I'll be free!

242
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,480
Be careful!

243
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,330
The formation has changed.

244
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,640
Senior!

245
00:12:05,090 --> 00:12:07,340
[Double-Spiritual Dragon-Locking Formation]

246
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:10,120
You're an evil dragon that harmed lives.

247
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:13,000
Considering that you were young and ignorant,

248
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:16,370
you were imprisoned underground
to atone for your sins.

249
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:19,640
Only when Beixin Bridge floods,

250
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,600
may you leave.

251
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:22,850
I was just passing by.

252
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,870
Those humans attacked me
because they were afraid.

253
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:27,550
What's wrong with me fighting back?

254
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:29,210
Beixin Bridge is not a bridge.

255
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:31,010
It will never flood.

256
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,160
So,

257
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:33,800
she can never leave.

258
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,840
That's unfair!

259
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:37,720
The evil dragon broke the formation
without permission.

260
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:39,680
She must be executed!

261
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:45,560
It's just a mechanical stone statue.

262
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:46,690
Talking is useless.

263
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,520
I'll think of something!

264
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:51,320
The array core.

265
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:53,030
If we destroy the core,

266
00:12:53,060 --> 00:12:54,500
we can stop the statues.

267
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,920
Damn it!

268
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:00,050
I can't do it without True Essence.

269
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:04,880
Chen Changsheng!

270
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,660
Without True Essence,

271
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,280
I can only succeed

272
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,640
at the Imperial Court Exam
if I achieve Seated Illumination.

273
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:14,310
Actually, I had no choice from the beginning.

274
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:17,960
No.

275
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,640
I can choose.

276
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,060
To do Seated Illumination

277
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,480
right here!

278
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:28,660
According to the book,

279
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,160
when observing within,

280
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,480
you'll see a pond.

281
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,280
Starlight melts into the pond water.

282
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,080
The pond water

283
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,240
flows along the stream

284
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,140
to every part of the body.

285
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:41,600
And this

286
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:44,440
is the image of my inner body.

287
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,440
Is my starlight

288
00:13:48,290 --> 00:13:51,330
[Sea of Qi Realm]

289
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:50,880
here?

290
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,240
There's no pond.

291
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,480
Only wind and snow.

292
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,560
So that's it.

293
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:13,120
It's not that I can't cultivate.

294
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:15,300
It's not that I have no starlight.

295
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:18,160
I have an entire snowfield!

296
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,620
Seated Illumination.

297
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,240
Ignite the stars!

298
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,760
With the Destiny Star's fire,

299
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:38,620
ignite ten thousand miles
of snow

300
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,370
and transform it into my True Essence!

301
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:01,000
[In the initial realm of Seated Illumination, a myriad of starlight kindled.
True Essence was tempered, and the heart is Approaching the Profound Truth]

302
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:15,670
[Heaven-Searing Sword]

303
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:21,480
This is the Realm of Seated Illumination.

304
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:24,280
This is what it feels like
to wield True Essence.

305
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:26,010
My body is full of power.

306
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:28,240
The techniques described in the Scriptures

307
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,860
come out naturally.

308
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:38,730
[Zhongshan Storm Sword: The World Upended]

309
00:15:45,730 --> 00:15:49,730
[Mountain spirits splits rocks]

310
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:05,920
Breaking through Seated Illumination
in such a short time.

311
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:07,380
You're truly impressive!

312
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,650
Unfortunately,

313
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,560
my meridians are broken.

314
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:16,970
They can't withstand
the burning transformation
of True Essence.

315
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:18,930
Defective meridians.

316
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,640
Starfire burns the body!

317
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:30,000
I finally

318
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:32,360
got to see that snowfield.

319
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,640
I can't give up.

320
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:41,440
Hang in there!

321
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:43,780
We need to break the formation together.

322
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,240
This colorless fire.

323
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,640
Even dragon breath can't suppress it.

324
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:50,840
How is that possible?

325
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:52,240
No.

326
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,720
Starfire burns from the inside out.

327
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:57,080
Why didn't he die instantly?

328
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,920
The heart is in the Profound Palace.

329
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,500
He didn't burn to death

330
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:04,440
because he has a heart that is already one
with the Profound Truth.

331
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,480
Colorless fire.

332
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:07,040
A heart that is already one
with the Profound Truth.

333
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:10,240
Could it be that he possesses a Stainless Body,
unseen in a thousand years?

334
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:12,400
Normal people go through Marrow Cleansing, Seated Illumination,
and then Approaching the Profound Truth.

335
00:17:11,319 --> 00:17:14,119
[Stainless Body]

336
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:16,960
He starts from Approaching the Profound Truth,
then Seated Illumination.

337
00:17:19,119 --> 00:17:20,880
Chen Changsheng.

338
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:23,849
At the root of it,

339
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:25,599
are you my fortune

340
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:27,720
or am I yours?

341
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,420
Starfire burning the body

342
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:30,680
is incurable.

343
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,200
There is only one way.

344
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,040
That is...

345
00:17:35,800 --> 00:17:37,660
to use the blood of the Dragon Race

346
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:39,440
to temper your body!

347
00:18:16,570 --> 00:18:21,160
The burning boy and the dragon.

348
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:18,940
[The Burning Boy and the Dragon]

349
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:22,620
[Episode 9]

350
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:26,320
You survived even this.

351
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:29,260
Looks like this place of death

352
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:31,480
is actually your blessed land.

353
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,400
Where am I?

354
00:18:41,520 --> 00:18:42,920
Why am I back?

355
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,920
I clearly already...

356
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,200
Who saved me?

357
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,000
This is...

358
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,280
True Essence?

359
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,930
Did I really succeed
in Seated Illumination?

360
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:08,920
Who ambushed me?

361
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:11,240
He came out of Director Chen's room.

362
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:12,400
I'm sorry.

363
00:19:12,630 --> 00:19:13,820
I just wanted to test it.

364
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:18,630
[Follow Your Heart]

365
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:15,680
This power...

366
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,460
Did you finish Seated Illumination?

367
00:19:19,560 --> 00:19:20,880
Sir!

368
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,320
Luo.

369
00:19:35,760 --> 00:19:38,420
That's the bell
for students entering the city.

370
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:40,140
It's the Imperial Court Exam!

371
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:42,520
Master.

372
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:43,760
Senior.

373
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:46,040
At last, this day has come.

374
00:19:49,010 --> 00:19:51,820
[The Imperial Court Exam begins]

375
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:56,830
[To be continued]

376
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,960
Follow Way of Choices animation.

377
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,420
Light up your Destiny Star.

378
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:03,400
We hope you all follow your heart.

379
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:09,010
[In the next episode]

380
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:08,160
Grand Pontiff destroyed
the State Religious Academy

381
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,360
yet allowed you to enroll.

382
00:20:09,360 --> 00:20:10,820
What exactly does he want?

383
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:11,930
I don't know.

384
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,400
But no matter what he's thinking,

385
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,360
I must win.

386
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,160
If I remember correctly,

387
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,620
this is not a martial exam.

388
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,200
If you want to blame someone,

389
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:21,560
blame yourself for angering everyone.

